{"tid":311590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［笑話]中印對峙 內地網民號召「抵制印度」結果......","createTime":"2017-07-06T17:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T23:09:48.000Z","uid":20058,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4f9de5c0c1d8af01eb0343dfb37eeb92d8bd77","tid":311590,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"印度與中國在錫金段的邊界糾紛持續，雙方對峙已20天。一如過去中國與其他國家爆發領土、安全爭端，內地網民近日紛紛呼籲「抵制印度」。但今次不同，喊抵制的網民陷入「空前困境」：究竟印度有什麼可給我們抵制......<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨天再回應中印邊界峙，重申印度軍隊「非法進入」中印邊界錫金段中方一側，「性質非常嚴重」，敦促印軍撤回自己一方。<br />\n<br />\n有什麼印度貨可抵制？<br />\n<br />\n官方措詞強硬，民間亦開始熱議。在新浪微博上，不少網民都喊起<span style=\"color: red;\">「抵制印度」、「抵制印貨」</span>口號，但旋即感到困窘，說「應該抵制印度點什麼呢？在線等，挺急的」！<br />\n<br />\n結果能答上的人不多，有人直言「我不清楚印度賣給我們什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民舉例，「雖遠必誅，鄰國太近，抵制印度神油，抵制印度飛餅」。惟有網民坦言，「印度神油我不用，飛餅我這輩子本來就沒吃過」，質疑怎抵制。</span><br />\n<br />\n有心水清的網民則提出，「印度在中國最出名的就是捷豹（Jaguar港譯積架）和路虎（Land Rover港譯越野路華）」。<br />\n<br />\nJaguar和Land Rove不太主流<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Jaguar和Land Rove上一任持有者為福特汽車，但2008年售與印度汽車製造商塔塔汽車公司，目前是其旗下「捷豹-荒原路華集團」的品牌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但網民卻指，「捷豹和路虎不像南韓知名品牌三星LG」，中國用的人不多，「想砸也不知哪裡找」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面對「愛國網民」的煩惱，有網民調侃說，「小粉紅這次有點安靜，也沒帝吧出征」，「抵制沒門兒，中國小紅粉的首次」。</span><br />\n<br />\n據了解，印度其實有不少出口產品，包括軟件、紅茶等農產品，但網民並無提及。<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1851023/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%20%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8D%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C......?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1851023%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%2520%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C......%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=iodypuAmUAvcHmHS27hSvC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fc45f94f\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1851023/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%20%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8D%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C......?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵制行動失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cecc9543b24f5b896fd25a8ef2d45074fc3040","tid":311590,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"抵制印度<br />\n<br />\n應該係唔食咖哩"},{"pid":"c338766428c358f621649e45f7d46cf78a5f0e9a","tid":311590,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"日本同香港咪一樣抵制唔到<br />\n垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a3573cf1a4450cd09afc3d26d5625212cb6da3","tid":311590,"uid":53705,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本同香港咪一樣抵制唔到<br />\n垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文其實係暗串印度 唔似得 日本, 韓國咁, 有咁多產品輸出中國/全世界<br />\n<br />\n所以抵制唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d2196397fa07750ff5eb67fae79d06f915bc24","tid":311590,"uid":12404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本同香港咪一樣抵制唔到<br />\n垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" c