生意來往<br />\n<br />\n二）點解大陸硬sell一戴一露<br />\n多幾個國家交易就多幾個國家可以抵制<br />\n話咁快統一天下"},{"pid":"e1bcc6b71b38c7f893f83e015027f353aa2f35fe","tid":311590,"uid":78349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"啲五毛spin撚到冇野比中國抵制係佢地既恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf943d24026deb9211c8eb512fd1a1f1082ae5b0","tid":311590,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"抵制失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f2bff3f7be630e68b7370f0263037d87a60e01","tid":311590,"uid":39521,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲五毛spin撚到冇野比中國抵制係佢地既恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地係靠內銷已經夠搵食，唔使輸出，自然冇野抵制<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實蝗蟈咪又係一樣，用佢地logic，蝗冇野值得鬼佬外國人抵制係咪奇恥大辱嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbc6223b348aa20904eb03f68d2b11e3e99daad","tid":311590,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"Jaguar Land Rover <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915eab7acbf2bae5df807dc4ff1c37f7f643e6bf","tid":311590,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Jaguar Land Rover <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來比印度收購左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba43372effa9baa6efe8925152f5683b3fc9506","tid":311590,"uid":39521,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Jaguar Land Rover <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來比印度收購左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實就算jag同land rover比印度佬收購咗，佢之前儲落嚟嘅design同reputation，都會令人覺得佢係british engineering<br />\n你估byd吉利做唔做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddce45a8c831c696934c04f94088fbb5a02c7f4","tid":311590,"uid":78253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:10:38.000Z","msg":"1. 西遊記猴神，佛教唔少神都係嚟自印度，大陸仔快抵制<br />\n<br />\n2. 大陸有無金援印度? 就自無都想投人哋D高鐵大型基建嚟做，快D抵制，等人哋可以安落揀日本支標啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0734e77d89c59f9d2c730453cda6c4f59c596cf7","tid":311590,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:14:44.000Z","msg":"如果講中國對外經濟制裁<br />\n最有效既係對北韓<br />\n果次侵侵響美國同習總第一次見面, 叫佢做野<br />\n之後中國威脅再核試就封鎖中朝邊境<br />\n金仔真心驚<br />\n你見到佢而家只係識射ICBM而唔搞核試就係驚呢樣野<br />\n因為習總無同侵侵寫包單金仔唔射飛彈, 所以任射"},{"pid":"d3ea1354e8a4363ed535bcd64d6e18352f7b2229","tid":311590,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個故事嘅教訓係<br />\n一）唔想做親咩都被人牽制嘅話<br />\n最好唔好同大陸有任何生意來往<br />\n<br />\n二）點解大陸硬sell一戴一露<br />\n多幾個國家交易就多幾個國家可以抵制<br />\n話咁快統一天下</blockquote><br />\n一)呢點成日講 做真係得啖笑 <br />\n<br />\n做生意都係講利潤成本 人地啲貨品質好 價錢岩 中國商佬會唔買咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36ce1424a3b88a85d9ff29805614ccdf4fbb7e0","tid":311590,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲五毛spin撚到冇野比中國抵制係佢地既恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地係靠內銷已經夠搵食，唔使輸出，自然冇野抵制<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實蝗蟈咪又係一樣，用佢地logic，蝗冇野值得鬼佬外國人抵制係咪奇恥大辱嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲五毛仲以為篇文係笑鳩印度<br />\n即刻喺樓上打晒飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad1e82fd0f2d0cc436dc879f2ce306497e6fc71","tid":311590,"uid":33216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"佛教唔係源自印度咩？"},{"pid":"64c47a